Class RemoteInputView.RemoteEditText

  • java.lang.Object
    • EditText
      • androidx.slice.widget.RemoteInputView.RemoteEditText
  • Enclosing class:
    RemoteInputView

    public static class RemoteInputView.RemoteEditText
extends EditText
    An EditText that changes appearance based on whether it's focusable and becomes un-focusable whenever the user navigates away from it or it becomes invisible.
